								<h1>IIM Bangalore</h1>
								<p>The Indian Institute of Management Bangalore (also known as IIMB) is a public business school located in Bangalore, Karnataka, India. Founded in 1973, it was the third IIM to be established, after IIM Calcutta and IIM Ahmedabad. It is consistently ranked as one of the best business schools in India and the Asia Pacific region. It offers a doctoral and several post graduate programmes, as well as a wide array of Executive training programmes. Vista is IIM Bangalore’s Annual flagship Business festival. The event is completely student-run and sees participation from across the country.</p></div>
